message.content: {"$schema":"https://json-schema.axonivy.com/process/12.0.0/process.json","id":"4BF7E2D1A59C3E07","description":"Process to handle new customer Slack message and leads","kind":"NORMAL","config":{"data":"com.axonivy.training.leads.LeadProcess"},"elements":[{"id":"f1","type":"SignalStartEvent","name":"Start: New Slack Message","config":{"output":"vars = new java.util.HashMap<>(); vars.put(\"customerMessage\", signal.message);"},"layout":{"at":{"x":100,"y":100}},"connect":[{"id":"f1_to_f2","to":"f2"}]},{"id":"f2","type":"EMail","name":"Notify Rolf about New Lead","config":{"headers":{"to":"rolf@axonivy.com","subject":"New lead from Slack"},"message":{"body":"We got a new lead from a Slack message.","contentType":"text/plain"}},"layout":{"at":{"x":300,"y":100}},"connect":[{"id":"f2_to_f3","to":"f3"}]},{"id":"f3","type":"Alternative","name":"Check License Cost","layout":{"at":{"x":500,"y":100}},"connect":[{"id":"f3_to_f4","condition":"vars.get(\"predictedLicenseCost\") != null && ((Double)vars.get(\"predictedLicenseCost\")) > 100000","to":"f4"},{"id":"f3_to_f5","condition":"vars.get(\"predictedLicenseCost\") == null || ((Double)vars.get(\"predictedLicenseCost\")) <= 100000","to":"f5"}]},{"id":"f4","type":"UserTask","name":"Assign High Priority Task to Marcel","config":{"task":{"priority":"HIGH","assignee":"marcel"}},"layout":{"at":{"x":700,"y":50}},"connect":[{"id":"f4_to_f5","to":"f5"}]},{"id":"f5","type":"TaskEnd","name":"End Process","layout":{"at":{"x":900,"y":100}}}],"docs":{},"layout":{"lanes":[{"name":"Slack Customer","lanes":[{"name":"Customer"}]},{"name":"Internal Team","lanes":[{"name":"Rolf"},{"name":"Marcel"}]}]}}
